WEBVTT

00:11.275 --> 00:16.012
Shoot, there's something I've been
trying to remember for the past few days.

00:16.046 --> 00:18.681
Was it that I'm halfway
between birthdays

00:18.716 --> 00:21.084
and you wanted to bake
me a half-birthday cake?

00:21.552 --> 00:22.886
That's a full cake.

00:22.921 --> 00:24.788
Don't let the word
"half" trick you.

00:25.222 --> 00:27.357
Daddy, stop trying to
take advantage of her.

00:27.391 --> 00:29.059
Hey, she lives here now.

00:29.093 --> 00:32.028
I can exploit her just like I
exploit the rest of you people.

00:33.631 --> 00:35.065
Sorry about that, Harper.

00:35.099 --> 00:36.499
But out of curiosity,

00:36.534 --> 00:38.501
were you gonna get me
a flat screen TV

00:38.536 --> 00:41.538
I could mount onto the ceiling?
I really hate sitting up.

00:41.572 --> 00:45.175
No, I don't think it...
Wait a minute.

00:46.310 --> 00:49.713
TV... TV...

00:49.747 --> 00:52.782
Oh, no fair!
You're gonna get a TV!

00:55.386 --> 00:59.189
TV... Stevie.

00:59.223 --> 01:02.692
Stevie! I think it had
something to do with Stevie.

01:02.727 --> 01:04.794
Our friend Stevie?

01:04.828 --> 01:07.764
Oh, was it that I wanted to borrow
her cute boots and that shredded top?

01:07.798 --> 01:10.200
I thought you were allergic
to other people's clothes.

01:10.234 --> 01:12.902
That's why you never
borrow mine.

01:12.937 --> 01:15.772
Why don't you jog her memory
with the "Jog Your Memory" spell?

01:15.806 --> 01:17.440
Oh, that's what
that spell does?

01:17.475 --> 01:19.109
I saw the word "jog"
and I bailed.

01:21.112 --> 01:22.712
<i>Do what you say
Say what you mean.</i>

01:22.747 --> 01:24.581
<i>One thing leads to another.
Remember!</i>

01:26.484 --> 01:29.619
I remember! Stevie took out
her wand and did a spell.

01:29.653 --> 01:30.854
She's a wizard!

01:30.888 --> 01:33.089
Oh, my gosh!
Stevie's a wizard?!

01:33.124 --> 01:36.159
Quick, Harper.
Bake a cake to celebrate.

01:37.294 --> 01:39.729
And just so we're clear,
that's two cakes.

